name: Dengar With Blaster Carbine
Lore: 'Corellian bounty hunter. Skilled athlete. Expert shot. Has worked many times for Jabba the Hutt. Carries a long-standing grudge against Han Solo.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Permanent weapon is •Dengar''s Blaster Carbine (may target a character, creature or vehicle for free; draw destiny; target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if destiny +1 > defense value; may be fired twice per battle).',
